         "title": "Daniela Ruah:‌ “I got the impostor syndrome, I get nervous every time. It started on gymnastics, I’d forget the routines at the carpet”",
         "description": "<p><span>In this first episode of Heart & Hustle: On Location, recorded at the International Portuguese Music Awards in Providence, Daniela sits down with Tony Gonçalves on rehearsal day to talk about what it really means to carry a culture with you, the imposter syndrome that never fully goes away, a childhood gymnastics story she'd never told publicly before, and why the IPMA has become something far bigger than a music awards show</span></p>",
